- `lib/models/daily_log_model.dart` – nutritionForAi, nutrition_summary
- `lib/models/meal_model.dart` – sottocollezione meals
- `lib/models/longevity_home_package.dart` – pacchetto unificato per Home AI
- `lib/services/nutrition_service.dart` – salvataggio Livello 1 + aggregation summary
- `lib/services/aggregation_service.dart` – Livello 2 (rolling), Livello 3 (baseline)
- `lib/services/ai_prompt_service.dart` – costruzione contesto da tutti e tre i livelli
- `lib/services/longevity_engine.dart` – pacchetto informativo Home (Livello 1+2+3)
